{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e07b0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3701"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3701"},"text":"§ 3701.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this chapter:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa2e07b1-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3701/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Cost or pricing data","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The term “cost or pricing data” means all facts that, as of the date of agreement on the price of a contract (or the price of a contract modification), or, if applicable consistent with ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s3706/a/2"},"text":"section 3706(a)(2) of this title","children":[],"tail":", another date agreed upon between the parties, a prudent buyer or seller would reasonably expect to affect price negotiations significantly. Such term does not include information that is judgmental, but does include the factual information from which a judgment was derived."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idaa3051a2-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s3701/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Subcontract","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The term “subcontract” includes a transfer of commercial products or commercial services between divisions, subsidiaries, or affiliates of a contractor or a subcontractor.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n